bilingual.source: Use a hydrometer to measure the density of the liquid.
bilingual.target: 使用测量液体密度的仪器来测量液体的密度。

bilingual.source: The density of this material is very high.
The forest has a high density of trees.
bilingual.target: 这片森林的树木密度很高。

bilingual.source: We need to measure the density of the liquid.
bilingual.target: 我们需要测量液体的密度。

bilingual.source: High-density materials are usually more durable.
bilingual.target: 高密度的材料通常更耐用。

bilingual.source: The density of the liquid changes with temperature.
bilingual.target: 液体的密度随温度变化。

bilingual.source: The population density in this area is very high.
bilingual.target: 这个地区的人口密度很大。

bilingual.source: This city has many high-density residential areas.
bilingual.target: 这个城市有很多高密度的住宅区。

bilingual.source: Engineers need to calculate the density of the structure.
bilingual.target: 工程师需要计算结构的密度。

bilingual.source: Scientists are studying the changes in air density.
bilingual.target: 科学家们正在研究空气的密度变化。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, come on. What's that? Oh, it's an Osteo National bone-density scanner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 算了吧，那是什么? 是国骨公司生产的骨质密度扫描仪。

yingyinNormal.en: Just under 27% of the rest of the energy density of the universe is made up of what we call dark matter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其他近27%的宇宙能量密度是由暗物质构成的。

yingyinNormal.en: That is true. I have a higher than normal body density. If I run too deep a bath, I drown.
yingyinNormal.zh: 确实如此我的体密度比平常人高，泡澡的水放太多，我都可能会淹死。

yingyinNormal.en: The remaining 68% of the energy density of the universe is made up of dark energy, which is even more mysterious than dark matter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 剩余68%的宇宙能量密度来自于暗能量，这种物质比暗物质更加神秘。

yingyinNormal.en: The material is a blend of taffeta and high density body armor. Fully armed and loaded. And they glow. That's nuclear.
yingyinNormal.zh: 由高档材料制作而成有高密度的盔甲防护，藏着上膛的武器，还有发着光的核武器。

yingyinNormal.en: That means it has the strange property that it expands as the volume of space increases to keep its energy density constant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那意味着暗能量具有一种特殊属性，它能够使暗能量随着宇宙体积的增长而扩大，从而使其能量密度保持不变。

yingyinNormal.en: Even though we see them all around us, the total energy density of these components is actually very small, around 5% of the total energy of the universe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尽管它们就在我们的周围，但这些组成部分的总能量密度却十分渺小，它们仅占整个宇宙总能量的5%左右。

yingyinNormal.en: When I took over this company for Dr. Pym, I immediately started researching a particle that could change the distance between atoms, while increasing density and strength.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当我从皮姆博士那里接手这家公司后，我立即开始研究一种能够改变原子间距离同时能增加密度和强度的粒子。

yingyinNormal.en: In here, you'll find emergency provisions. An eight day supply of food and water, a crossbow, season 2 of Star Trek the original series on a high density flash drive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在这里，你可以找到应急储备，足够八天的食物和水，一把弩，一个高密度优盘，里面有原版的《星际迷航》第二季。

yingyinNormal.en: Which suggests either a remarkable passivity among the, I assume, 24 to 36 residents of this building, based on the number of mailboxes and given typical urban population density or a shared delusion of functionality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就说明要么这楼的24到36户人家，我假设的，基于邮箱的个数和典型的城市人口密度得出的都特别懒散，要么都同时产生功能性错觉。

yingyinNormal.en: Despite Singapore's high urban density, the island is incredibly fertile.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虽然新加坡是个人口稠密的都市，岛上土地却十分肥沃。

exam_freq_info.chinese: 密集; 密度; 浓度

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Reduce the <highlight>density</highlight> of some of its forests.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 减少一些森林的密集程度。

examination_example.sentence: Half a century of town and country planning has enabled it to retain an enviable rural coherence, while still permitting low-<highlight>density</highlight> urban living.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 半世纪以来的城乡规划使其得以保留令其他国家羡慕的乡村协调性，同时还允许低密度的城镇人口。

examination_example.sentence: The resulting settlement maps show how the distribution and <highlight>density</highlight> of the rural population around the city changed between AD 500 and 850.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 由此产生的聚居点地图显示了在公元500年到850年之间，城市周围的乡村人口分布和密度是如何发生变化的。
